did.abstract: This collections contains the records of the Internation Brotherhood of Teamsters Communications Department dating from 1958-1983. Included are publications distibuted by the department dating from 1977-1983 and minutes of the General Executive Board from 1958-1959.

arrangement.p: Organized into two series: Publications and Newspaper Clippings; Publications are further divided into two subseries, Teamsters Division Publications and Teamsters Division Pamplets and Printed Materials.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collections contains the records of the Internation Brotherhood of Teamsters Communications Department dating from 1958-2011. Included are publications distibuted by the department dating from 1963-2011 and minutes of the General Executive Board from 1957-1958.

bioghist.head: Biographical / Historical
bioghist.p: The Communications Department works closely with International Union departments, divisions, and affiliates to spread information on union programs and goals to members, their families, retirees, allied organizations, public officials, the news media, and the general public. The department also promotes Teamsters concerns and campaigns to the news media, and responds to media inquiries.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by publication, then chronologically.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This series contains publications distributed by the International Brotherhood of Teamsters Communications Department.

The monthly publication of the Communications Department was the Teamsters News Service which was distributed throughout the organization with the purpose of informing other Teamsters publications about important events or announcements. Common features would include collections of relevant political cartoons and tips for IBT publication editors. This collection also includes pamphlets, handouts, and other English, French, and Spanish-language materials developed by the Teamsters Communication Department.
